<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Funds Received</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .email-header {
            background-color: #b9b6ac;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .email-header img {
            max-width: 150px;
        }

        .email-body {
            padding: 20px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .email-body h1 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .email-body p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .email-footer {
            background-color: #aaa69e;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .transaction-details {
            background-color: #a7a69d;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .transaction-details p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-body h1 {
                font-size: 20px;
            }

            .email-body p {
                font-size: 14px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dzybjyiku/image/upload/v1732189212/47c1ef85da8ba758aef568df072e8f13.png"
                alt="Bakare Fin Pay">
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <h1>Funds Received!</h1>
            <p>Hello <%= recipient %>,</p>
            <p>You have received a sum of <strong>
                    <%= currency %>
                        <%= amount %>
                </strong> from <%= sender %>. Below are the details of the transaction:
            </p>
            <div class="transaction-details">
                <p><strong>Amount Received:</strong>
                    <%= currency %>
                        <%= amount %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Sender:</strong>
                    <%= sender %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Transaction Date:</strong>
                    <%= transactionDate %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Transaction ID:</strong>
                    <%= transactionId %>
                </p>
            </div>
            <p>The funds have been successfully added to your wallet. You can use them immediately for transactions or
                withdrawals.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            &copy; 2024 Bakare Fin Pay. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>